# Rules specific for this project

- New features must be created inside the `src/modules/<feature-name>/` directory.
- Each module should contain the following subfolders:
  - `components/` – UI elements unique to this module.
  - `hooks/` – Custom hooks for encapsulated logic.
  - `services/` – API or domain logic specific to this module.
  - `types/` – Module-specific TypeScript types or interfaces.
- Common/shared components should go in `src/shared/`.
